<HEADLINE> Karachi Stock Exchange Index Drops </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, June 9 (Xinhua) -- The Karachi Stock Exchange
(KSE)-100 Index Tuesday dropped by 12.27 points to close at
1075.24 against last Friday's close of 1,087.51 points.
</P>
<P>
A total volume of 29.78 million shares was traded Tuesday
against last Friday's turnover of 46.37 million shares.
</P>
<P>
There were 51 gainers and 62 losers while 32 scrips remained
unchanged. 
</P>
