the moderates believed that he would be convicted by the
conservative judiciary though he has denied all the charges
against him.
</P>
<P>
According to the Majlis regulations, Nouri should give his
explanation before the Majlis within 10 days after the proposed
motion for the impeachment was submitted.
</P>
<P>
"By impeaching the interior minister, the right wing in the
Majlis can no more claim to be supporting Khatami's government,"
the Iran News daily on Monday quoted a moderate parliamentarian as
saying.
</P>
<P>
Observers here believed that political struggles between the
two rival factions have entered a sensitive stage as both sides
openly blast at each other and some conservatives even fingered at
Khatami and former President Hashemi Rafsanjani. 
