<HEADLINE> Gold Price in Hong Kong Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, June 10 (Xinhua) -- The gold price in Hong Kong
dropped by 28 HK dollars to close at 2,690 HK dollars a tael
Wednesday, according to Po Sang Bank, one of the major gold
dealers in Hong Kong.
</P>
<P>
The gold price is equivalent to 291.42 U.S. dollars a troy
ounce, 3.04 U.S. dollars less than the previous close at
Wednesday's exchange rate of one U.S. dollar to 7.7485 HK
dollars. 
