<HEADLINE> Int'l Building, Construction Exposition Opens in HK </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, June 10 (Xinhua) -- The International Building and
Construction Exposition (IBEX'98) opened here on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Also opened in the Hong Kong Convention and Exhibition Center,
in conjunction with the IBEX'98, were the International Security,
Protection and Safety Exposition and the International Building
Fitting, Finishes and Interior Decoration Exposition.
</P>
<P>
The three-day event provides a marketing platform for more than
200 companies from over 10 countries and regions. Italy has been
participating in IBEX for the 15th time, ever since the event's
inaugural presentation in 1979.
</P>
<P>
From this year on, the traditionally biennial event organized
by the Reed Exhibition Ltd. will be turned annual.
</P>
<P>
As this year's event was the first IBEX presentation since Hong
Kong's handover to China in July last year, it was more focused on
highlighting the trade links with China's inland areas. A
presentation on the development of China's building industry set
for Thursday has registered over 200 participants who are
interested in the China market.
</P>
<P>
The organizers had decided that next year's IBEX will mainly
cover building materials, products and services.
</P>
<P>
And, following last year's success, the Hong Kong Construction
Association, the Hong Kong Institution of Engineers, the Hong Kong
Institute of Builders and Reed Exhibition Companies has organized
another seminar during IBEX'98. 
</P>
