at 210.44 million Singapore dollars (122.35 million U.S. dollars).
Declines led advances by 290 to 44 while 256 other counters
remained unchanged.
</P>
<P>
Easyknit remained the most actively traded stock as it
registered a turnover of 11.69 million units. It was followed by
DBS Land which had 7.701 million shares traded. SingTel, that had
6.86 million shares changed hands, took the third place.
</P>
