UOB topped the gainers list of the day as it rose by 25 cents
to finish at 6.10 Singapore dollars. DCBC F increased by 20 cents
to end at 5.95 Singapore dollars. DBS F was up by 15 cents to
close at 9.40 Singapore dollars.
</P>
<P>
On the downside, SPH was the biggest loser as it declined by 70
cents to end at 11.50 Singapore dollars. Both Bukit Sem and
Creative 50 fell by 40 cents and closed at 8.50 and 28.00
Singapore dollars respectively. 
