<TEXT>
<P>
TIANJIN, June 10 (Xinhua) -- The first non-state-owned science
park opened recently at the Tanggu Marine High-tech Park near
Tianjin.
</P>
<P>
The science park covers an area of 400,000 square meters. It
has good transport facilities as it is adjacent to Tianjin Harbor,
the railway trunk between Beijing and Harbin, an expressway and
the Binhai Airport.
</P>
