<HEADLINE> Chinese Vice-Premier Meets Norwegian FM </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, June 10 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Vice-Premier Qian Qichen
met with Norwegian Foreign Minister Knut Vollebaek here today.
</P>
<P>
They exchanged views on expanding bilateral relations of
friendship and cooperation and international issues of common
interest.
</P>
<P>
Vollebaek is here at the invitation of China's Ministry of
Justice to attend the second round-table meeting on justice
between the two countries. 
</P>
