<HEADLINE> Thai Airways Ranks First in Service Survey </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Bangkok, June 10 (Xinhua) -- Thai Airways International was
voted the carrier with the most efficient inflight services and
high quality catering in a recent International Air Transport
Association (IATA) survey.
</P>
