<TEXT>
<P>
NANJING, June 10 (Xinhua) -- Aon Corp. Bain Hogg Group
Plc, an insurance firm from the United States, has set up a
representative office in east China's Jiangsu Province.
</P>
<P>
As the first foreign-funded insurance agent office ever set up
in the province, it will help promote Sino-overseas cooperation in
the insurance sector and spur the province's economic development,
said a local official.
</P>
